{"tid":624972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"食環署瑞和街執法　燒臘檔夥計躁爆","createTime":"2018-04-11T05:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T05:29:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"48551063672ce69c9344c9676f12a4707bc64aaf","tid":624972,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T05:29:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180411/20358392?_ga=2.12176052.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180411%2F20358392%3F_ga%3D2.12176052.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=a3%2FA6laLgyZZ0mbNJ%2FLrwk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=e4e9386e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180411%2F20358392%3F_ga%3D2.12176052.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=c634ebb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180411/20358392?_ga=2.12176052.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n食環署瑞和街執法　燒臘檔夥計躁爆<br />\n<br />\n5.9K<br />\n港聞<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】 食環署人員昨午1時許到觀塘瑞和街執法，其間懷疑一間燒臘檔有物件阻街，於是採取行動，但燒臘檔職員不服，與食環署人員發生爭執，附近店舖有職員亦加入戰團，爆粗大罵食環署人員，事件引來大批途人圍觀。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報後派出手持盾牌的警員到場調查，經調停後協助食環署人員離開，事件中無人受傷，無人被捕。"}]}